data.description: Seller will accept or counter offers between $399,500 and $414,500. Be the proud owner of this lovely 2-story property in the desirable Countryside Village! Featuring desert front yard & 2-car garage w/extended driveway. The charming interior boasts a sizable living room adjacent to a bright dining room, making entertaining a bliss. Spacious family room opens to the well-kept kitchen, fully equipped w/granite counters, white cabinetry, a convenient pantry, recessed lighting, SS appliances, & an island w/breakfast bar. The practical den is ideal for home office, while the spacious loft is perfect for media room. Sizable main retreat has a full bathroom w/dual sinks & walk-in closet. Low-maintenance backyard w/mountain views & extended covered patio is ideal for relaxing.
